{"tid":1814292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日先叫緊唔好捉鬼 而家又喺度話勇武退出嘅係鬼","createTime":"2020-01-07T00:41:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T02:59:01.000Z","uid":61886,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8da5d12309c630bc2474fbc55a503e6729bd3188","tid":1814292,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:41:05.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢哋係智力低定係冇思考能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武退出聲明<br />\n講緊就係唔好捉鬼<br />\n呢個係佢哋我哋嘅訊息<br />\n我哋應該好好思考<br />\n都要學習避免呢個情況<br />\n<br />\n另一方面<br />\n勇武退出係一直都有嘅事<br />\n被捕 受傷 每日都發生緊<br />\n仲有幾多小隊係完完整整晒人<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得勇武退出係冇發生緊<br />\n咁樣只係自欺欺人<br />\n一廂情願覺得勇武可以無條件付出所有嘢<br />\n<br />\n與其喺度思考呢啲聲明係真定假<br />\n不如咁啦我哋可以做啲乜嘢<br />\n去持續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n七千人被捕係不爭嘅事實<br />\n抗爭既模式 時間 溫度 <br />\n點樣維持 點樣改變 點樣進化<br />\n係我哋需要面對嘅事實<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋只係覺得會有無限勇武既幻想<br />\n咁你就要認清呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n利申 小隊仍然努力中<br />\n<br />\n希望各位<br />\n唔好再執着無謂嘅真假<br />\n不如推下行動post<br />\n有幾多人知今個星期有乜嘢抗爭嘅活動"},{"pid":"62df7559d601d282aa8310285e488eca561ef56d","tid":1814292,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:44:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"412acaab251b9f100253c729e2576bb9c45fcc2d","tid":1814292,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fe440eb5b94c32cffc5543358dda4c79aea4c22","tid":1814292,"uid":239842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:46:25.000Z","msg":"又小隊<br />\n真係冇人想知，靜啦。"},{"pid":"1f0d8a30e9eb23e1f975ee3b06e20ac8ad3249c7","tid":1814292,"uid":204479,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:46:38.000Z","msg":"連登平均年齡16歲 你想有咩思考能力"},{"pid":"2117f6143967519bd5ef6981de4530aa8d812507","tid":1814292,"uid":276715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:47:36.000Z","msg":"五毛帶風向姐<br />\n大家拉到就拉"},{"pid":"ad00308801619abf2493bd70c8c91c3979230d35","tid":1814292,"uid":188282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:50:22.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n話你知有300隊成立緊"},{"pid":"4cd3b65636896a66dd85856eac4eceab3dfce544","tid":1814292,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:51:53.000Z","msg":"其實同被自殺一樣，對面一定會溝啲假嘅落去，搞到每一單分唔到真假，混淆視聽，再推波助瀾，大家就屌嚟屌去，希望只係小風波，唔會有大影響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋打仗，兵唔補就只會越嚟越少，各位嘈完就諗下點樣一人行多一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f02ef6639736ab25fd5aca4f17adff36ac2f05","tid":1814292,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:53:03.000Z","msg":"全隊拉哂死剩我，所以我上連登唱通街比多啲線索共產黨拉埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我寧願真勇武唔好上連登，不被捕重要過有人安慰<br />\n<br />\n再唔好講連登起低捉5毛係㩒個制就睇到哂，點同現場捉鬼"},{"pid":"3b941e6ca286fe8784f15d4210406c5c1c8b634f","tid":1814292,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe440eb5b94c32cffc5543358dda4c79aea4c22","tid":1814292,"uid":239842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:46:25.000Z","msg":"又小隊<br />\n真係冇人想知，靜啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"其實係藍球小隊"},{"pid":"ce2c103b5cd7e7e81bbf6775637e33eaad7fcaf4","tid":1814292,"uid":206617,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:53:31.000Z","msg":"其實呢個時候仲話緊勇武退出聲明係帶風氣、鬼、分化，根本就同捉鬼個心態冇咩分別<br />\n話完全冇勇武受捉鬼影響根本自欺欺人<br />\n憑咩要人地老鳳用條命黎抗爭？<br />\n和理非有負擔，勇武就冇？<br />\n<br />\n睇住自己手足一個一個俾人拉、俾人打，跟手仲要俾你班&ldquo;和理非&rdquo;屈係鬼<br />\n心灰想退出，退出前呻下、屌下你地班捉鬼撚都唔得？<br />\n連登仔講野慣左不負責任，係到屌啲聲明打擊軍心之前，又可唔可理解下自己既捉鬼屈毛係幾咁撥人冷水？"},{"pid":"29b14d56dbd98ddc18f193d4168efa77f5d29502","tid":1814292,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:53:54.000Z","msg":"無人想知"},{"pid":"e4712234e3a3046d33d6008474c4ed70cf59c5fd","tid":1814292,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:54:02.000Z","msg":"如果捉鬼嘅本身係鬼呢，黑警心諗呢招真係好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ee675af32d459c185f10670d6230aac4571981","tid":1814292,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4712234e3a3046d33d6008474c4ed70cf59c5fd","tid":1814292,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:54:02.000Z","msg":"如果捉鬼嘅本身係鬼呢，黑警心諗呢招真係好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"其實個概念等於<br />\n幾個月前五毛扮和理非同勇武喺度鬧交一樣<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解而家仲會有人中計"},{"pid":"fcadb4a1f422b2a6b682a9c280ce3a79aae82ffa","tid":1814292,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8da5d12309c630bc2474fbc55a503e6729bd3188","tid":1814292,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:41:05.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢哋係智力低定係冇思考能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武退出聲明<br />\n講緊就係唔好捉鬼<br />\n呢個係佢哋我哋嘅訊息<br />\n我哋應該好好思考<br />\n都要學習避免呢個情況<br />\n<br />\n另一方面<br />\n勇武退出係一直都有嘅事<br />\n被捕 受傷 每日都發生緊<br />\n仲有幾多小隊係完完整整晒人<br />\n<br />\n唔好覺得勇武退出係冇發生緊<br />\n咁樣只係自欺欺人<br />\n一廂情願覺得勇武可以無條件付出所有嘢<br />\n<br />\n與其喺度思考呢啲聲明係真定假<br />\n不如咁啦我哋可以做啲乜嘢<br />\n去持續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n七千人被捕係不爭嘅事實<br />\n抗爭既模式 時間 溫度 <br />\n點樣維持 點樣改變 點樣進化<br />\n係我哋需要面對嘅事實<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋只係覺得會有無限勇武既幻想<br />\n咁你就要認清呢個事實<br />\n<br />\n利申 小隊仍然努力中<br />\n<br />\n希望各位<br />\n唔好再執着無謂嘅真假<br />\n不如推下行動post<br />\n有幾多人知今個星期有乜嘢抗爭嘅活動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:57:03.000Z","msg":"樓主為你好，靜d 喇，好多mon post sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda8cedcfa8deb3a1c1dee96e6d228be9748451f","tid":1814292,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T00:58:49.000Z","msg":"解散言論就算真又好假又用<br />\n我只會用黎警惕自己有咩自己可以做多d<br />\n希望大家都係咁<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n遊行集會請幫手叫新口號<br />\n「手足好珍貴<br />\n唔好再捉鬼」"},{"pid":"37878fc83a2b951cd1377d6ee5704e88a50bd9ea","tid":1814292,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:00:49.000Z","msg":"捉鬼基因對e班人黎講係咪永生不能磨滅既呢<br />\n又返魂走黎屈手足係鬼"},{"pid":"8d7e431a69ac50df34205a3ba411593b50f67ded","tid":1814292,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T02:59:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200107/SVNPQ76IGX5DHVNXBVQMLCSTUA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR22bbvJAHNSdJedtA4usWMOK-cDzgzhciK_NeSw4IImQtBenE2b2_7xTlg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200107%2FSVNPQ76IGX5DHVNXBVQMLCSTUA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR22bbvJAHNSdJedtA4usWMOK-cDzgzhciK_NeSw4IImQtBenE2b2_7xTlg&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=765e3153\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200107%2FSVNPQ76IGX5DHVNXBVQMLCSTUA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR22bbvJAHNSdJedtA4usWMOK-cDzgzhciK_NeSw4IImQtBenE2b2_7xTlg&h=dfe7e596\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200107/SVNPQ76IGX5DHVNXBVQMLCSTUA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR22bbvJAHNSdJedtA4usWMOK-cDzgzhciK_NeSw4IImQtBenE2b2_7xTlg</a><br />\n「Do your best in what you do best。無論咩身位都好，唔需要將自己變成另一個人；要諗自己最叻係做咩，然後去做嗰樣嘢。」<br />\n退出就退出，搵到更好既position咪去做。"}]}